# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# uDOS v1.3 Multi-Installation Architecture .gitignore
# Clean Distribution Repository - User Content Isolation
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🎯 uDOS DISTRIBUTION STRATEGY
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ✅ Keep: Core system, installation types, shared resources, wizard dev tools
# 🚫 Exclude: User content, personal data, session logs, sandbox activity
# 🔄 Sync: Only Dev Mode changes to core system components

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🔒 USER CONTENT ISOLATION - NEVER IN DISTRIBUTION
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 🔐 Level 1: uMEMORY - Personal Archive System (NEVER in repo)
# Contains user missions, moves, memories, milestones, daily session data
uMEMORY/
uMEMORY.backup/
uMEMORY/*/

# 🔐 Level 2: Sandbox - Active User Workspace (NEVER in repo)
# Where most user activity occurs before archiving to uMEMORY
sandbox/user.md
sandbox/user/
sandbox/experiments/
sandbox/drafts/
sandbox/tasks/in-progress/
sandbox/tasks/completed/
sandbox/scripts/active/
sandbox/scripts/executed/
sandbox/archived-tests/
sandbox/personal/
sandbox/**/*.working
sandbox/**/*.tmp

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🏢 MULTI-INSTALLATION USER DATA ISOLATION
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Installation-specific user data (not core installation functionality)
installations/wizard/user-data/
installations/wizard/personal/
installations/wizard/session-logs/
installations/sorcerer/user-projects/
installations/sorcerer/personal-configs/
installations/imp/user-projects/
installations/imp/personal-scripts/
installations/drone/user-tasks/
installations/drone/personal-automation/
installations/tomb/user-archives/
installations/tomb/personal-backups/
installations/ghost/user-demos/
installations/ghost/personal-sandbox/

# Shared user-specific configurations (not system defaults)
shared/user-configs/
shared/personal/
shared/**/*.user
shared/**/*.personal

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🛠️ DEVELOPMENT ISOLATION - DEV MODE ONLY
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ✅ KEEP: wizard/notes/ - Development logs in hex format (ALWAYS SYNC)
# These contain development progress and are part of the distribution
# wizard/notes/ - SYNCED TO GIT

# 🚫 EXCLUDE: Personal wizard development sessions
wizard/personal/
wizard/user-sessions/
wizard/.dev-session-*
wizard/**/*.personal
wizard/**/*.user
wizard/**/*.working

# Development environment temporary files
wizard/**/*.tmp
wizard/**/*.log
wizard/**/*.cache

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🚫 BUILD ARTIFACTS & COMPILATION OUTPUT
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Build and compilation artifacts
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.so
*.out
*.exe
dist/
build/
out/

# Package manager files and dependencies
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
package-lock.json
.npm/
.yarn/

# Python virtual environments (uSCRIPT venv system)
uSCRIPT/venv/
**/venv/
**/.venv/
*.venv

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📦 LARGE ASSETS & DEMO CONTENT
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Large demo files and assets (should be downloaded separately during installation)
**/demo-content/
**/large-assets/
**/sample-data/
**/test-data/
**/fonts/*.ttf
**/fonts/*.ttc
**/media/*.gif
**/media/*.mp4
**/media/*.avi
**/media/*.mov
**/media/*.webm
*.iso
*.img

# Generated/downloaded content during installation
downloads/
cache/
temp-downloads/
installation-downloads/

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📝 LOGS & TEMPORARY FILES
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# System and application logs (not development logs in wizard/notes/)
**/*.log
*.tmp
*.working
*.cache
validation-*.log
test.log
test-*.log
test-output-*
gemini-*.log
installation-*.log
session-*.log

# User-generated logs (different from core system logs)
user-*.log
personal-*.log
sandbox-*.log
**/user-logs/
**/session-logs/

# Temporary processing files
*.processing
*.temp
temp-*
processing-*

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 💻 SYSTEM & OS FILES
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# macOS system files
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
.ipynb_checkpoints/
Thumbs.db
.localized

# Linux/Unix hidden files
.*~
.*.swp
.*.swo

# Windows system files
desktop.ini
*.lnk

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📦 DISTRIBUTION & PACKAGING ARTIFACTS
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Distribution archives and packaging
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.dmg
*.vsix
*.deb
*.rpm
uDOS-v*.tar.gz
uDOS-v*.zip
uDOS-distribution-*
release-*

# Installation artifacts (generated during user installation)
install-udos.log
installation.log
validation-*.log
user-config.local
setup-complete.flag
installation-report.txt
system-info.txt

# Generated distribution packages and builds
release/
dist-packages/
packaging/
builds/
uCORE/launcher/uDOS.app/Contents/
uCORE/launcher/build/
uCORE/launcher/*.dmg
uCORE/launcher/uDOS_installation.log

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ⚙️ EDITOR & IDE CONFIGURATIONS
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Personal VS Code settings (keep workspace shared settings)
.vscode/settings.json
.vscode/launch.json
.vscode/tasks.json
# Keep: .vscode/extensions.json, .vscode/workspace.code-workspace

# Environment and authentication
.env
.env.local
.env.user
.gemini/
~/.gemini/
.anthropic/
.openai/

# IDE personal configurations
.idea/
*.sublime-*
.atom/

# wizard wizard development environment - personal logs and sessions
wizard/logs/
wizard/summaries/
wizard/.dev-session-*
*.uLOG

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# �️ EDITOR & IDE ARTIFACTS
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# VS Code personal settings and workspace
.vscode/
.env
.env.local

# Gemini CLI authentication
.gemini/
~/.gemini/

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📱 DISTRIBUTION ARTIFACTS (built locally)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Generated distribution packages
release/
dist-packages/
uCORE/launcher/uDOS.app/Contents/
uCORE/launcher/build/
uCORE/launcher/*.dmg
uCORE/launcher/uDOS_installation.log

# Local user modifications and configs
user.config
local.settings
*.user.md
personal-*.md

# Generated documentation exports
exports/
generated-docs/

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🧪 TESTING & DEVELOPMENT ENVIRONMENTS
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Test environments and temporary testing
/tmp/
temp/
testing/
scratch/
test-environments/
**/test-runs/
**/test-results/

# User-specific development configurations
config.local.*
settings.local.*
user.config
local.settings
*.user.md
personal-*.md

# Generated documentation exports (not core docs)
exports/
generated-docs/
user-exports/

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🗑️ CLEANUP & MAINTENANCE
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Trash system - Archived and deprecated files
# This folder is tracked to maintain cleanup history and system evolution
trash/

# Backup files created during maintenance
*.backup
*.bak
*.old
*~

# uMEMORY backup archives (keep directory structure, exclude backup files)
**/backup/*.tar.gz
**/backup/*.zip
**/backup/*-umemory-backup.*
**/backup/*-sandbox-backup.*
**/backup/umemory-backup-report.md

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ✅ uDOS v1.3 DISTRIBUTION INCLUDES
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ✅ uCORE/ - Core system architecture and utilities
# ✅ installations/ - Multi-installation framework (6 role types)
# ✅ shared/ - Cross-installation resources and default configurations  
# ✅ docs/ - Complete system documentation and guides
# ✅ extension/ - VS Code extension development framework
# ✅ install/ - Installation scripts for all platforms
# ✅ wizard/notes/ - Development logs in hex format (ALWAYS SYNCED)
# ✅ wizard/tools/ - Development utilities and workflows
# ✅ wizard/utilities/ - System utilities for development
# ✅ uKNOWLEDGE/ - Shared knowledge base system
# ✅ uSCRIPT/ - Production script management system
# ✅ sandbox/README.md - Workspace templates and task management framework
# ✅ Core files: README.md, LICENSE, CHANGELOG.md, .gitignore
# ✅ Shared workspace configuration: .vscode/extensions.json, workspace files

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🚫 uDOS v1.3 DISTRIBUTION EXCLUDES  
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🚫 uMEMORY/ - User personal archive (missions, moves, memories, milestones)
# 🚫 sandbox/user* - Active user workspace and personal content
# 🚫 installations/*/user-* - Installation-specific user data
# 🚫 wizard/personal/ - Personal development sessions
# 🚫 shared/user-* - User-specific shared configurations
# 🚫 All *.log files except core system logs
# 🚫 All personal, temporary, and build artifacts
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
